{"tid":693302,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣自駕] 嘉義 - 開車往阿里山-路況","createTime":"2018-06-07T11:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T14:43:23.000Z","uid":100555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ee52ff10f5c541a31d7970386212b0930da1f1","tid":693302,"uid":100555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"第一次開POST<br />\n各位巴打, 我7月想自駕台灣, 係網絡上做左D資料搜索, 阿里山的自駕情況<br />\n有D人話好危險, 有D人話而家路況好左, 慢開就得<br />\n個心十五十六, 不知道到底咩情況<br />\n所以先問問大家, 到底現在自駕上去阿里山情況怎樣?<br />\n1) 會有好多遊覽車 (大巴) 在路上嗎? 有沒有什麼時間開比較少車的?<br />\n2) 路寬嗎? 會有好多沙石影響駕駛嗎?<br />\n3) 有什麼需要注意嗎?<br />\n唔該哂各位巴打先"},{"pid":"453c636cd19de0962b8a1ba589f02d4afdf7c0d1","tid":693302,"uid":78313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"早兩個月去過<br />\n不過台21上台18落<br />\n有雙程路都唔算好窄<br />\n大巴多數早上上山<br />\n遇到大巴會頂住<br />\n因常大巴通常好守規矩行30<br />\n落石又冇遇過<br />\n不過周圍都有牌叫人提防落石<br />\n要注意就係阿里山部分道路係進行維護工程<br />\n久唔久會封路一個鐘<br />\n最好上網查定先"},{"pid":"cfe43a43317810267a4330610442629a3e094f99","tid":693302,"uid":100555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"453c636cd19de0962b8a1ba589f02d4afdf7c0d1","tid":693302,"uid":78313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"早兩個月去過<br />\n不過台21上台18落<br />\n有雙程路都唔算好窄<br />\n大巴多數早上上山<br />\n遇到大巴會頂住<br />\n因常大巴通常好守規矩行30<br />\n落石又冇遇過<br />\n不過周圍都有牌叫人提防落石<br />\n要注意就係阿里山部分道路係進行維護工程<br />\n久唔久會封路一個鐘<br />\n最好上網查定先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:44:16.000Z","msg":"多謝你回覆先<br />\n我想問你會唔會有下面類似的情況出現? 我睇片見到D大巴好似好顛咁...<br />\n所以先驚驚地<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/12MuA-aqOGA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F12MuA-aqOGA&d=49PVwSL8tEzP4Prf3PHnqUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ea2c9848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/12MuA-aqOGA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=avWkNHtGZ88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DavWkNHtGZ88&d=49PVwSL8tEzP4Prf3PHnqUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6d2a9adb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=avWkNHtGZ88</a><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪慢慢開, 上落行18線都應該安全呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7df88b7c76527f8701d8bbb3998669b4ca26a9","tid":693302,"uid":78313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"咁我又冇見過d大巴咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常山路都好慢<br />\n如果咁岩跟住大巴尾會安全<br />\n不過就好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n18好行過21<br />\n冇咁崎嶇"},{"pid":"c5ca7114411fc5407cba9fce434b0ffbb77bfb76","tid":693302,"uid":100555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa7df88b7c76527f8701d8bbb3998669b4ca26a9","tid":693302,"uid":78313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"咁我又冇見過d大巴咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常山路都好慢<br />\n如果咁岩跟住大巴尾會安全<br />\n不過就好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n18好行過21<br />\n冇咁崎嶇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"想問巴打你係咪揸開車？定係去旅行先楂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef401efc20fc300acb4a5a3c3d12446668480ad0","tid":693302,"uid":100555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5ca7114411fc5407cba9fce434b0ffbb77bfb76","tid":693302,"uid":100555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa7df88b7c76527f8701d8bbb3998669b4ca26a9","tid":693302,"uid":78313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"咁我又冇見過d大巴咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常山路都好慢<br />\n如果咁岩跟住大巴尾會安全<br />\n不過就好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n18好行過21<br />\n冇咁崎嶇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"想問巴打你係咪揸開車？定係去旅行先楂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\